problem.markdown:
>> CNNs were introduced to encourage neural networks to focus on _________ in images. <<

[[
sharpness {{While CNNs can learn to focus on sharpness, it may learn to focus on other aspects.}}
global features {{Global features are more complex and unique to images, which makes them harder to learn.}}
(local features) {{CNNs focus on local features and build up complex representations of images by composing these local features together through multiple layers.}}
brightness {{While CNNs can learn to focus on brightness, it may learn to focus on other aspects.}}
